    {
      "Text": "An update for postfix is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3",
      "Title": "Summary",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "Postfix is a Mail Transport Agent (MTA).\n\nSecurity Fix(es):\n\nPostfix before 3.8.16, 3.9 before 3.9.10, and 3.10 before 3.10.9 sometimes allows a buffer over-read and process crash via an enhanced status code that lacks text after the third number.(CVE-2026-43964)",
      "Title": "Description",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "An update for postfix is now available for openEuler-24.03-LTS-SP3.\n\nopenEuler Security has rated this update as having a security impact of low. A Common Vunlnerability Scoring System(CVSS)base score,which gives a detailed severity rating, is available for each vulnerability from the CVElink(s) in the References section.",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
      "Text": "Low",
      "Title": "Severity",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
